---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTASection from "../components/CTASection.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — GameBoard.live"
  description="GameBoard.live is building the simplest way to run a live sports scoreboard from your phone."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>We make game day simple</h1>
      <p>
        GameBoard.live started courtside, watching volunteers wrestle with clunky
        consoles and paper score sheets. We thought keeping score should be as easy
        as picking up your phone.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to give every club, school and tournament organiser a
        scoreboard that works on the hardware they already have — a phone to control
        it, any screen to show it, and a link to share it with the crowd.
      </p>

      <h2>What we believe</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Simple beats powerful.</strong> The fastest tool is the one people actually use.</li>
        <li><strong>No special hardware.</strong> Your phone and a screen are enough.</li>
        <li><strong>Built with clubs.</strong> Every feature comes from real game-day feedback.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        We're in early access and building in the open. If that sounds like your
        kind of team, we'd love to have you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem);
  }
  h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }
  ul {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  ul strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
